=Description=

'''Our Vision''': Create a Seamlessly Connected Relationship Economy

'''Our Mission''': To Maximize the Value of a Relationship-Driven Economy through never ending improvement of systems, education and collaboration with all stakeholders

'''Our Strategic Objectives''':

1) Create a common body of knowledge from all stakeholders (corporations, entrepreneurs & investors, consultants & trainers, recruiters, member-based organizations, educational institutions and governmental agencies) as to what needs to improve most to least

2) Facilitate Collaboration for the benefit of all stakeholders

3) Develop educational forums and curriculum for early adopters as well as professional networkers both individually and organizationally

4) Enable all stakeholders to maximize their value proposition and economic return in a relationship economy

5) Celebrate Progress and Innovation 


